Summer Purrs & Winter Woofs This duo of bubble teas blends vibrant summer energy with winter’s cool calm. The tangy orange drink bursts with citrus zest, while the refreshing blueberry drink mixes sweetness with refreshing mint. The flavors will have you purring and woofing!

Soup Noodles and Ramune by the Beach
